history.provenance: Written in France around the 1460's. Early provenance unknown. On fol. 53r: "Margueritte dela Linde 1618 et/ Jehanne [Morterre] 1618"; Catalogue entry glued to inside cover; longhand catalogue entry on paper glued to fol. iv; on fol. iir, in lead: "On Sale Atkinson Jan 28-22."
